vernac_cmds: Require Import Recdef Coqlib Maps Errors.
Record typenv : Type := Typenv { te_typ: PTree.t T.t; te_equ: list constraint }.
Definition initial : typenv := {| te_typ := PTree.empty _; te_equ := nil |}.

Definition set (e: typenv) (x: positive) (ty: T.t) : res typenv := match e.(te_typ)!x with | None => OK {| te_typ := PTree.set x ty e.(te_typ); te_equ := e.(te_equ) |} | Some ty' => if T.eq ty ty' then OK e else Error (MSG "bad definition/use of variable " :: POS x :: nil) end.

Fixpoint set_list (e: typenv) (rl: list positive) (tyl: list T.t) {struct rl}: res typenv := match rl, tyl with | nil, nil => OK e | r1::rs, ty1::tys => do e1 <- set e r1 ty1; set_list e1 rs tys | _, _ => Error (msg "arity mismatch") end.

Definition move (e: typenv) (r1 r2: positive) : res (bool * typenv) := if peq r1 r2 then OK (false, e) else match e.(te_typ)!r1, e.(te_typ)!r2 with | None, None => OK (false, {| te_typ := e.(te_typ); te_equ := (r1, r2) :: e.(te_equ) |}) | Some ty1, None => OK (true, {| te_typ := PTree.set r2 ty1 e.(te_typ); te_equ := e.(te_equ) |}) | None, Some ty2 => OK (true, {| te_typ := PTree.set r1 ty2 e.(te_typ); te_equ := e.(te_equ) |}) | Some ty1, Some ty2 => if T.eq ty1 ty2 then OK (false, e) else Error(MSG "ill-typed move from " :: POS r1 :: MSG " to " :: POS r2 :: nil) end.

Fixpoint solve_rec (e: typenv) (changed: bool) (q: list constraint) : res (typenv * bool) := match q with | nil => OK (e, changed) | (r1, r2) :: q' => do (changed1, e1) <- move e r1 r2; solve_rec e1 (changed || changed1) q' end.
Lemma move_shape: forall e r1 r2 changed e', move e r1 r2 = OK (changed, e') -> (e'.(te_equ) = e.(te_equ) \/ e'.(te_equ) = (r1, r2) :: e.(te_equ)) /\ (changed = true -> e'.(te_equ) = e.(te_equ)).
destruct e.(te_typ)!r1 as [ty1|]; destruct e.(te_typ)!r2 as [ty2|]; inv H; simpl.
Lemma length_move: forall e r1 r2 changed e', move e r1 r2 = OK (changed, e') -> length e'.(te_equ) + (if changed then 1 else 0) <= S(length e.(te_equ)).
destruct e.(te_typ)!r1 as [ty1|]; destruct e.(te_typ)!r2 as [ty2|]; inv H; simpl.
Lemma length_solve_rec: forall q e ch e' ch', solve_rec e ch q = OK (e', ch') -> length e'.(te_equ) + (if ch' && negb ch then 1 else 0) <= length e.(te_equ) + length q.
destruct a as [r1 r2]; monadInv H.
set (X := (if ch' && negb (ch || ch0) then 1 else 0)) in *.
set (Z := (if ch' && negb ch then 1 else 0)) in *.
destruct ch'; destruct ch; destruct ch0; simpl; auto.
Definition weight_typenv (e: typenv) : nat := length e.(te_equ).

Function solve_constraints (e: typenv) {measure weight_typenv e}: res typenv := match solve_rec {| te_typ := e.(te_typ); te_equ := nil |} false e.(te_equ) with | OK(e', false) => OK e | OK(e', true) => solve_constraints e' | Error msg => Error msg end.
Definition makeassign (e: typenv) : typassign := fun x => match e.(te_typ)!x with Some ty => ty | None => T.default end.
Definition solve (e: typenv) : res typassign := do e' <- solve_constraints e; OK(makeassign e').
Definition satisf (te: typassign) (e: typenv) : Prop := (forall x ty, e.(te_typ)!x = Some ty -> te x = ty) /\ (forall x y, In (x, y) e.(te_equ) -> te x = te y).
Lemma satisf_initial: forall te, satisf te initial.
unfold initial; intros; split; simpl; intros.
Lemma set_incr: forall te x ty e e', set e x ty = OK e' -> satisf te e' -> satisf te e.
destruct H0 as [A B]; simpl in *.
Lemma set_sound: forall te x ty e e', set e x ty = OK e' -> satisf te e' -> te x = ty.
Lemma set_list_incr: forall te xl tyl e e', set_list e xl tyl = OK e' -> satisf te e' -> satisf te e.
induction xl; destruct tyl; simpl; intros; monadInv H; eauto with ty.
Lemma set_list_sound: forall te xl tyl e e', set_list e xl tyl = OK e' -> satisf te e' -> map te xl = tyl.
induction xl; destruct tyl; simpl; intros; monadInv H.
Lemma move_incr: forall te e r1 r2 e' changed, move e r1 r2 = OK(changed, e') -> satisf te e' -> satisf te e.
destruct (te_typ e)!r1 as [ty1|] eqn:E1; destruct (te_typ e)!r2 as [ty2|] eqn:E2.
inv H; simpl in *; split; auto.
inv H; simpl in *; split; auto.
inv H; simpl in *; split; auto.
Lemma move_sound: forall te e r1 r2 e' changed, move e r1 r2 = OK(changed, e') -> satisf te e' -> te r1 = te r2.
destruct (te_typ e)!r1 as [ty1|] eqn:E1; destruct (te_typ e)!r2 as [ty2|] eqn:E2.
Lemma solve_rec_incr: forall te q e changed e' changed', solve_rec e changed q = OK(e', changed') -> satisf te e' -> satisf te e.
destruct a as [r1 r2]; monadInv H.
Lemma solve_rec_sound: forall te r1 r2 q e changed e' changed', solve_rec e changed q = OK(e', changed') -> In (r1, r2) q -> satisf te e' -> te r1 = te r2.
destruct a as [r3 r4]; monadInv H.
Lemma move_false: forall e r1 r2 e', move e r1 r2 = OK(false, e') -> te_typ e' = te_typ e /\ makeassign e r1 = makeassign e r2.
unfold makeassign; destruct (te_typ e)!r1 as [ty1|] eqn:E1; destruct (te_typ e)!r2 as [ty2|] eqn:E2.
Lemma solve_rec_false: forall r1 r2 q e changed e', solve_rec e changed q = OK(e', false) -> changed = false /\ (In (r1, r2) q -> makeassign e r1 = makeassign e r2).
destruct a as [r3 r4]; monadInv H.
Lemma solve_constraints_incr: forall te e e', solve_constraints e = OK e' -> satisf te e' -> satisf te e.
intros te e; functional induction (solve_constraints e); intros.
Lemma solve_constraints_sound: forall e e', solve_constraints e = OK e' -> satisf (makeassign e') e'.
intros e0; functional induction (solve_constraints e0); intros.
Theorem solve_sound: forall e te, solve e = OK te -> satisf te e.
Lemma set_complete: forall te e x ty, satisf te e -> te x = ty -> exists e', set e x ty = OK e' /\ satisf te e'.
Lemma set_list_complete: forall te xl tyl e, satisf te e -> map te xl = tyl -> exists e', set_list e xl tyl = OK e' /\ satisf te e'.
induction xl; intros; inv H0; simpl.
exploit (set_complete te e a (te a)); auto.
Lemma move_complete: forall te e r1 r2, satisf te e -> te r1 = te r2 -> exists changed e', move e r1 r2 = OK(changed, e') /\ satisf te e'.
assert (Q': forall x y, In (x, y) ((r1, r2) :: te_equ e) -> te x = te y).
destruct (te_typ e)!r1 as [ty1|] eqn:E1; destruct (te_typ e)!r2 as [ty2|] eqn:E2.
Lemma solve_rec_complete: forall te q e changed, satisf te e -> (forall r1 r2, In (r1, r2) q -> te r1 = te r2) -> exists e' changed', solve_rec e changed q = OK(e', changed') /\ satisf te e'.
exploit (move_complete te e r1 r2); auto.

Lemma solve_constraints_complete: forall te e, satisf te e -> exists e', solve_constraints e = OK e' /\ satisf te e'.
exploit (solve_rec_complete te (te_equ e) {| te_typ := te_typ e; te_equ := nil |} false).
exploit (solve_rec_complete te (te_equ e) {| te_typ := te_typ e; te_equ := nil |} false).
Lemma solve_complete: forall te e, satisf te e -> exists te', solve e = OK te'.
destruct (solve_constraints_complete te e H) as (e' & P & Q).
